}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000435",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Fach Niveau Sek II (BY)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2522"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote" : [ {
    "@value" : "in Bayern genannt Anforderungsniveau"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000438",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Curriculum aggregates a set of curriculum items, each providing means for the systematic planning and structuring of teaching and learning materials, as well as the instructional methods used within an education system or educational institution. It can be considered as a detailed plan that outlines the learning objectives, teaching materials, instructional strategies, assessment criteria, and time frame for a particular course, subject, or educational level. A curriculum refers to a specific subject, school type, grade level(s) and form of expression (major/minor, 1st/2nd/3rd foreign language, etc.)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lehrplan umfasst eine Reihe von Lehrplan-Elementen, die jeweils als Mittel für die systematische Planung und Strukturierung von Lehr- und Lernmaterialien sowie die in einem Bildungssystem oder einer Bildungseinrichtung verwendeten Lehrmethoden dienen. Der Lehrplan kann als Leitfaden betrachtet werden, der die Lernziele, Lehrmaterialien, Unterrichtsstrategien, Beurteilungskriterien und den Zeitrahmen für einen bestimmten Kurs, ein Fach oder eine Bildungsstufe umreißt. Der Lehrplan bezieht sich auf ein bestimmtes Unterrichtsfach, Schulform, Klassenstufe(n) und Ausprägungsform (Hauptfach/Nebenfach, 1./2./3. Fremdsprache, usw.)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lehrplan"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000440",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000438"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "für_bildungsgangabschnitt"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000811"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lehrplan Element bezogen auf den Lehrplan von Berlin und Brandenburg"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Element (BE/BB)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2526"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Die Unterschiede zw. Berlin und Brandenburg müssten evtl. noch mal genauer geprüft werden. Ggf. sind die Klassen hier noch zu trennen."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000442",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "competence is a competence item, which expresses a capability an individuum already inheres or aquires throughout a learning process"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Kompetenz (BE)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2532"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Competence is generally understood as the combination of knowledge and skills in coping with the demands of action. Persons are considered competent if they are able to regenerate currently required actions on the basis of knowledge, skills and abilities. \nInstances of this class provide text that describes a particular competence (e.g. \"reading\")."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000443",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Berlin/Brandenburg grouping of educational levels in stages A-G."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Unterteilung der Jahrgangsstufen in Niveaustufen A-G in Berlin/Brandenburg Lehrplänen."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Niveaustufe (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "bb educational grade"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Für Grundschulen und Grundstufen der Gemeinschaftsschulen sowie an\nweiterführenden Schulen mit den Jahrgangsstufen 5 und 6 gilt:\n\n* Schulanfangsphase = Niveaustufen A, B, in Teilen C\n* Jahrgangsstufen 3 – 4 = Niveaustufe C, in Teilen D\n* Jahrgangsstufe 5 = Niveaustufen C – D\n* Jahrgangsstufe 6 = Niveaustufe D, in Teilen E\n\nSchülerinnen und Schüler mit dem sonderpädagogischen Förderbedarf Lernen\nwerden auf folgenden Niveaustufen unterrichtet:\n* Jahrgangsstufe 3 = Niveaustufe B, in Teilen C\n* Jahrgangsstufen 4 – 6 = Niveaustufe C\n* Jahrgangsstufen 7 – 8 = Niveaustufe D\n* Jahrgangsstufen 9 – 10 = Niveaustufen D – E\n\nFür die Integrierte Sekundarschule gilt:\ngrundlegendes Niveau:\n* Jahrgangsstufen 7 – 8 = Niveaustufen D – E, in Teilen F\n* Jahrgangsstufen 9 – 10 = Niveaustufe F, in Teilen G\n* erweitertes Niveau:\n* Jahrgangsstufen 7 – 8 = Niveaustufe E, in Teilen F\n* Jahrgangsstufen 9 – 10 = Niveaustufen F – G"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000444",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lehrplan (BE)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2536"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000445",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lerninhalt (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "learning content"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2544"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel" : [ {
    "@value" : "Inhalt (BE)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Learning content that is taught as part of teaching. The learning content can be linked to competences that the learner can acquire while learning the content."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lerninhalt der im Rahmen des Unterrichts vermittelt wird. Der Lerninhalt kann mit Kompetenzen verknüpft sein, die die lernende Person beim Lernen des Inhalts erlangen kann."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000446",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Lernmaterial (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "learning material"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2548"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Konkrete Mittel (z.B. in Form von Dokumenten), um bestimmte Kompetenzen zu erlernen."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Some concrete means (e.g in form of documents) to acquire particular competences."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000447",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Competence is generally understood as the combination of knowledge and skills in coping with the demands of action. Persons are considered competent if they are able to regenerate currently required actions on the basis of knowledge, skills and abilities. \nInstances of this class provide text that describes a particular competence (e.g. \"reading\")."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "operationalisierbar und meßbar"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Standard (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "competence"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2552"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid2564"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel" : [ {
    "@value" : "Abschlussorientierter Standard (BE)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "competence is a competence item, which expresses a capability an individuum already inheres or aquires throughout a learning process"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000448",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Thema (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "topic"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2568"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A concrete topic of school teaching that can be taught through particular learning content."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Ein konkretes Thema des Unterricht, das durch Lerninhalte vermittelt werden kann."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000449",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Themenfeld (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "topic area"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000441"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2572"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel" : [ {
    "@value" : "Themenbereich (BE)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A topic area includes one or more topics that are subject of teaching."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Ein Themenfeld umfasst ein oder meherere Themen die im Unterricht behandelt werden."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000450",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Zusatzmaterial (BE)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "additional material"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid2576"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Documents which refer to additional resources to learn with."
  }, {
    "@language" : "de",
    "@value" : "Dokumente, die auf zusätzliche Ressourcen zum Lernen verweisen."
  } ]
}, {
